text: Carl Eiríksson was a sports shooter from Iceland. Eiríksson competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics. He was born on 29 December 1929 and died on 12 June 2020.Carl Eiríksson == References == Category:1929 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Icelandic sportspeople Category:Sport shooters Category:Olympians
